# Database Schema Visualization

## Core Entities ERD

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User ||--o{ Conversation : "owns"
    User ||--o{ ApiKey : "has"
    User ||--o{ Device : "owns"
    User ||--o{ Memory : "stores"
    User ||--o{ TopicProfile : "creates"
    User ||--o{ EntityProfile : "defines"
    User ||--o{ ContextSettings : "configures"
    User ||--o{ VirtualUser : "is"

    VirtualUser ||--o{ Conversation : "captures"

    Conversation ||--o{ Message : "contains"
    Conversation ||--o{ AtomicChatUnit : "segmented into"
    Conversation ||--o{ ContextBundle : "bundles"
    Conversation ||--o{ TopicConversation : "belongs to"
    Conversation ||--o{ ImportedConversation : "is"

    Message ||--o{ AtomicChatUnit : "extracted from"
    Message ||--o{ MessageStylePreset : "uses"

    TopicProfile ||--o{ TopicConversation : "has"
    EntityProfile ||--o{ EntityConversation : "has"

    AtomicChatUnit ||--o{ TopicConversation : "linked to"
    AtomicChatUnit ||--o{ EntityConversation : "linked to"
    AtomicChatUnit }|..|{ Memory : "related to"
```

## Key Database Models

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class User {
        +String id PK
        +String? displayName
        +String? email
        +String? avatarUrl
        +DateTime createdAt
        +DateTime updatedAt
        +DateTime lastSeenAt
        +Json settings
        +Json privacyPreferences
    }

    class Conversation {
        +String id PK
        +String provider
        +String sourceUrl
        +String? contentHash
        +Int version
        +String title
        +String? model
        +String state
        +String visibility
        +DateTime createdAt
        +DateTime updatedAt
        +DateTime capturedAt
        +Int messageCount
        +Json metadata
        +String[] tags
        +String? ownerId FK
        +String? virtualUserId FK
    }

    class Message {
        +String id PK
        +String conversationId FK
        +String role
        +String? author
        +Json parts
        +String? contentHash
        +Int version
        +DateTime createdAt
        +Int messageIndex
        +String status
        +Json renderedContent
    }

    class AtomicChatUnit {
        +String id PK
        +String content
        +String type
        +String category
        +String state
        +Float importance
        +String authorDid
        +Float[] embedding
        +String conversationId FK
        +String messageId FK
        +String? topicProfileId FK
        +String? entityProfileId FK
    }

    class ContextBundle {
        +String id PK
        +String userId FK
        +String bundleType
        +String compiledPrompt
        +Int tokenCount
        +Json composition
        +Int version
        +Boolean isDirty
        +DateTime? compiledAt
    }

    class Memory {
        +String id PK
        +String userId FK
        +String content
        +String category
        +Float importance
        +Float[] embedding
        +Boolean isActive
        +DateTime createdAt
    }

    class TopicProfile {
        +String id PK
        +String userId FK
        +String slug
        +String label
        +Float[] embedding
        +Json metadata
    }

    class EntityProfile {
        +String id PK
        +String userId FK
        +String name
        +String type
        +Float[] embedding
        +Json metadata
    }

    class ContextSettings {
        +String id PK
        +String userId FK
        +Int maxContextTokens
        +String? defaultPriorityLayer
        +String? embeddingModel
        +Float? temperature
        +Json preferences
    }

    class VirtualUser {
        +String id PK
        +String did
        +String userType
        +String publicKey
        +String? encryptedPrivateKey
        +String state
        +Json metadata
        +DateTime createdAt
    }

    User "1" --> "*" Conversation
    User "1" --> "*" Memory
    User "1" --> "*" TopicProfile
    User "1" --> "*" EntityProfile
    User "1" --> "1" ContextSettings
    Conversation "1" --> "*" Message
    Conversation "1" --> "*" AtomicChatUnit
    Message "1" --> "*" AtomicChatUnit
    AtomicChatUnit "1" --> "*" ContextBundle
```

