## Schema Versioning

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> v1_initial
    
    v1_initial --> v2_users: Add users table
    v2_users --> v3_conversations: Add conversations & messages
    v3_conversations --> v4_acu: Add ACU support
    v4_acu --> v5_vector: Add vector embeddings
    v5_vector --> v6_bundles: Add context bundles
    v6_bundles --> v7_rights: Add rights layer
    v7_rights --> v8_advanced: Add advanced features

    note right of v1_initial: Initial schema
    note right of v2_users: User management
    note right of v3_conversations: Core data
    note right of v4_acu: Memory extraction
    note right of v5_vector: Semantic search
    note right of v6_bundles: Context assembly
    note right of v7_rights: T0-T5 tiers
    note right of v8_advanced: Latest features
```

